# ISIIC Image Classification: Melanoma vs. Benign

## Overview
This Jupyter Notebook provides a simple implementation of an image classification system to distinguish between melanoma and benign skin lesions using a deep learning model. The model utilizes the **International Skin Imaging Collaboration (ISIC)** dataset.

